	error MSB4096: The item "CoreML.framework" in item list "NativeReference" does not define a value for metadata "FrameworkFilename".  
	In order to use this metadata, either qualify it by specifying %(NativeReference.FrameworkFilename), 
	or ensure that all items in this list define a value for this metadata.
